  "prompt": "How do I watch Formula 1 online in India?",
  "response": "As of my last update, fans in India can watch Formula 1 online primarily via the Disney+ Hotstar streaming service. Disney+ Hotstar holds the broadcasting rights for Formula 1 in India, and they typically offer both live streaming of the races and on-demand content, including highlights and analysis.\n\nHere is how you can watch Formula 1 on Disney+ Hotstar:\n\n1. **Subscription**: First, you need to have a subscription to Disney+ Hotstar. The platform usually offers various subscription plans, so you can choose one that suits your preferences.\n\n2. **Device**: You can watch the races on multiple devices, including smartphones, tablets, laptops, or smart TVs, by downloading the Disney+ Hotstar app or visiting their website.\n\n3. **Login**: Once you have a subscription, log in to your Disney+ Hotstar account using your credentials.\n\n4. **Search for F1**: Use the search function to find live Formula 1 races or related content.\n\n5. **Schedule**: Remember to check the race schedule and set reminders for live events, as race timings may vary due to the different time zones.\n\nPlease note that broadcasting rights can change, so it's a good idea to verify the current broadcast partner and available platforms periodically.",
